name: Oktoviuς
description:
The wisdom messenger

Serving as a messenger between multiverses as well as the great advisor of the alpha.  Using "the eye" which he always holds on to his tentacles to find out who the message will be sent to.  His horns were glistening and filled with wisdom.  Won't feel thirst and hunger, can't be seen by people he won't send messages to.

If you see him, he will send you a message.
